00:05:19.340 --> 00:05:20.540
Then we can cook spicy dishes.

00:05:20.700 --> 00:05:21.660
Hot and sour noodles.

00:05:22.900 --> 00:05:23.940
Boiled fish in spicy soup.

00:05:24.100 --> 00:05:25.460
Mapo tofu.

00:05:25.460 --> 00:05:26.460
Spicy chicken cubes.

00:05:26.460 --> 00:05:28.020
Spicy boiled blood curd.

00:05:33.100 --> 00:05:33.940
Auntie,

00:05:33.950 --> 00:05:35.740
