- Mr. Lin...
- Yeah, what about this arrow wound?

00:17:52.460 --> 00:17:53.300
It's alright.

00:17:54.340 --> 00:17:55.700
I'll be fine after dealing with it.

00:17:56.300 --> 00:17:57.580
The top priority right now

00:17:58.210 --> 00:17:59.180
is to leave here

00:17:59.660 --> 00:18:00.620
and return to Yong'an.

00:18:01.130 --> 00:18:02.140
Alright, alright.

