we can't report it to the authorities.

00:18:13.850 --> 00:18:15.140
What if we leave him here

00:18:15.240 --> 00:18:16.700
and he gets eaten by beasts?

00:18:17.000 --> 00:18:18.180
His identity is so special.

00:18:18.540 --> 00:18:19.660
Why bother with him?

00:18:19.660 --> 00:18:20.700
If beasts don't mind,

00:18:20.700 --> 00:18:22.240
it could be considered his good fortune.

00:18:22.620 --> 00:18:24.060
Someone will find him soon.

00:18:24.420 --> 00:18:25.260
Let's go.

00:18:25.300 --> 00:18:26.690
Liu Chang will come to meet us soon.

00:18:26.690 --> 00:18:27.460
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:18:27.460 --> 00:18:28.700
- Stay close together.
- Hurry.

00:18:28.700 --> 00:18:30.060
I don't want to stay here any longer.

00:18:30.060 --> 00:18:31.020
- Quick.
- Quick, Yangyang.

00:18:31.020 --> 00:18:31.860
Go, go, go.

00:18:39.980 --> 00:18:40.820
Speed up.

00:18:44.140 --> 00:18:46.820
(Virtue and Fragrance)

00:18:53.620 --> 00:18:54.660
It's just a minor injury.

00:18:55.570 --> 00:18:57.260
I can recover without taking medicine.

00:18:57.820 --> 00:18:59.020
Take the medicine first.

00:19:02.380 --> 00:19:03.220
Wait a minute.

00:19:03.500 --> 00:19:04.820
Your hand isn't convenient to use.

00:19:05.540 --> 00:19:06.380
Let me help you.

00:19:12.340 --> 00:19:13.340
I can do it myself.

00:19:17.500 --> 00:19:19.340
My father and mother couldn't
bear it anymore.

00:19:19.660 --> 00:19:20.900
They have to rest first.

00:19:21.820 --> 00:19:23.340
Yangyang was frightened.

00:19:24.380 --> 00:19:25.740
My brother must stay with her.

00:19:27.420 --> 00:19:29.140
If you need something, just let me know.

00:19:45.700 --> 00:19:46.540
Does it hurt?

00:19:49.060 --> 00:19:49.900
No, it doesn't.

00:20:17.820 --> 00:20:18.660
Sorry.

00:20:23.100 --> 00:20:23.940
Let me do it.

00:20:27.340 --> 00:20:31.180
(Qingyang Cui Case)

00:20:51.020 --> 00:20:52.900
No idea who wrote this file.

00:20:53.100 --> 00:20:55.040
This person must be good
at writing compositions.

00:20:55.180 --> 00:20:56.690
He can get full marks for presentation.

00:20:57.500 --> 00:20:59.530
Composing and writing
mean the same thing.

00:21:00.330 --> 00:21:01.500
Writing compositions?

00:21:02.220 --> 00:21:03.060
Isn't the meaning

00:21:03.580 --> 00:21:04.700
repeated?

00:21:04.820 --> 00:21:05.860
Ignore it.

00:21:05.860 --> 00:21:06.900
The point is

00:21:07.140 --> 00:21:08.820
his presentation is very neat.

00:21:08.820 --> 00:21:10.900
Ordinary people don't write articles
that carefully.

00:21:10.900 --> 00:21:12.740
There will be some signs
of modification.

00:21:12.860 --> 00:21:13.860
But he didn't.

00:21:14.020 --> 00:21:15.540
As if it had been recopied.

00:21:21.740 --> 00:21:23.300
(Qingyang Cui Case)

00:21:23.300 --> 00:21:26.460
(To be punished by the death penalty.)

00:21:29.980 --> 00:21:32.180
(Cao Mansion)

00:21:32.180 --> 00:21:35.900
(Qingyang Cui Case)

00:21:35.900 --> 00:21:37.540
(Harboring ill intentions)

00:21:37.540 --> 00:21:38.700
Just as you said,

00:21:39.220 --> 00:21:42.500
this file has no errors or omissions.

00:21:42.620 --> 00:21:44.540
This is obviously a recopy.

00:21:45.660 --> 00:21:47.060
I was blinded by a single leaf.

00:21:47.300 --> 00:21:49.240
I had been delving
into the contents of the file,

00:21:49.240 --> 00:21:50.100
yet I never expected

00:21:50.100 --> 00:21:52.860
that the key information lay
beyond the words themselves.

00:21:53.860 --> 00:21:55.740
The case was so urgent back then.

00:21:55.760 --> 00:21:57.110
Yet Master Xiao still took the time

00:21:57.110 --> 00:21:58.180
to copy it out deliberately

00:21:58.190 --> 00:22:01.040
and submit it to the Capital Prefecture
and the Court of Judicial Review.

00:22:01.060 --> 00:22:02.880
He must have secrets
that must be kept hidden.

00:22:06.110 --> 00:22:06.950
Unfortunately,

00:22:07.900 --> 00:22:09.900
Master Xiao is now in a coma.

00:22:10.200 --> 00:22:11.490
We can't get anything out of him.

00:22:14.140 --> 00:22:15.380
Fifth Master Xiao

00:22:15.490 --> 00:22:18.300
is a taciturn person
who won't say a word.

00:22:19.260 --> 00:22:21.340
However, he was very diligent
in writing.

00:22:21.340 --> 00:22:24.140
Not only would he carry a tablet
when attending court meetings,

00:22:24.140 --> 00:22:25.830
but even while eating or walking,

00:22:26.010 --> 00:22:27.850
he would bring different kinds of slips

00:22:28.300 --> 00:22:30.260
to record events that occurred.

00:22:30.620 --> 00:22:32.100
So some people made fun of him,

00:22:32.100 --> 00:22:34.220
saying he was no different
from those attendants

00:22:34.220 --> 00:22:37.220
who constantly recorded the daily life
of His Majesty.

00:22:37.220 --> 00:22:38.380
They gave him a nickname,

00:22:38.380 --> 00:22:40.220
Attendant Prince Consort.

00:22:41.650 --> 00:22:42.900
So I suppose

00:22:43.290 --> 00:22:44.740
when he was investigating the case,

00:22:44.980 --> 00:22:47.420
he would also carry a slip
to record events.

00:22:56.750 --> 00:22:57.820
If Prince Consort Xiao

00:22:58.180 --> 00:23:00.620
left behind that slip,

00:23:01.260 --> 00:23:02.700
perhaps there will be new clues.

00:23:05.260 --> 00:23:06.100
By the way,

00:23:06.160 --> 00:23:07.850
(Secret letter)
Prince Zhao sent a letter,

00:23:07.860 --> 00:23:10.580
saying that the hunt for the Shen family
was all Li Ang's nonsense.

00:23:10.800 --> 00:23:12.190
He has already been taught a lesson.

00:23:14.980 --> 00:23:15.820
When I was young,

00:23:16.740 --> 00:23:17.820
even as a feudal prince,

00:23:18.140 --> 00:23:19.460
if he felt he was wrong,

00:23:19.700 --> 00:23:21.340
he would apologize to me.

00:23:21.500 --> 00:23:23.660
I assumed that since he was reasonable

00:23:23.660 --> 00:23:24.820
and free of airs,

00:23:25.440 --> 00:23:26.740
he must be a fair-minded person.

00:23:27.040 --> 00:23:28.990
Now he shifts all the responsibility
onto Li Ang.

00:23:29.500 --> 00:23:30.540
This is just a tactic,

00:23:31.160 --> 00:23:33.020
the same as when he showed sincerity

00:23:34.660 --> 00:23:35.940
toward me.

00:23:36.800 --> 00:23:38.480
In the case
of selling official positions,

00:23:38.500 --> 00:23:40.620
many of the traded posts
were in the Ministry of War.

00:23:41.060 --> 00:23:41.900
Perhaps,

00:23:42.460 --> 00:23:44.420
they are not after money at all.

00:23:45.100 --> 00:23:47.140
If the ears, tongues, mouths, and eyes
in the court

00:23:47.420 --> 00:23:48.700
are all replaced by others,

00:23:49.740 --> 00:23:50.580
that person

00:23:51.180 --> 00:23:52.620
would become a true 'lonely ruler'.

00:23:53.060 --> 00:23:53.900
Young Master,

00:23:54.100 --> 00:23:55.180
I don't quite understand

00:23:55.660 --> 00:23:57.380
what you mean by that.

00:23:57.700 --> 00:23:58.540
I mean

00:23:59.100 --> 00:23:59.940
Prince Zhao

00:24:00.340 --> 00:24:01.900
may be related to all of this.

00:24:02.580 --> 00:24:03.620
His Majesty is aged

00:24:04.020 --> 00:24:06.100
and still has a few brothers
in their prime.

00:24:06.690 --> 00:24:08.460
Who could benefit from the case?

00:24:11.050 --> 00:24:12.820
If that were really the case,

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:14.510
Prince Zhao would certainly not want us

00:24:14.520 --> 00:24:16.070
to continue investigating.

00:24:16.310 --> 00:24:17.880
Even if there are many suspicious points

00:24:17.880 --> 00:24:19.140
about Prince Zhao,

00:24:20.100 --> 00:24:21.560
that is still not enough to conclude

00:24:21.890 --> 00:24:23.980
that he was involved
in that incident back then.

00:24:27.500 --> 00:24:28.420
Forget it for now.

00:24:28.860 --> 00:24:29.700
At present,

00:24:29.710 --> 00:24:30.990
Prince Zhao also dared not rashly

00:24:30.990 --> 00:24:32.260
extend his reach into Yong'an.

00:24:32.810 --> 00:24:33.820
He wrote this letter

00:24:34.410 --> 00:24:35.660
to keep us steady.

00:24:35.740 --> 00:24:37.060
Both sides have their concerns.

00:24:37.440 --> 00:24:38.790
The other party got anxious first.

00:24:39.320 --> 00:24:40.940
Naturally, they'll lose their composure.

00:24:40.940 --> 00:24:43.220
Then would it be more appropriate for us

00:24:43.220 --> 00:24:44.740
to send the Shen family away first?

00:24:54.420 --> 00:24:55.500
Greetings, Mr. Lin.

00:24:58.380 --> 00:24:59.580
We came to see

00:25:00.040 --> 00:25:01.620
if your injury has gotten any better.

00:25:01.980 --> 00:25:02.940
No major issues remain.

00:25:03.220 --> 00:25:04.420
Thanks for your concern.

00:25:05.060 --> 00:25:05.900
Come in and sit.

00:25:08.470 --> 00:25:09.920
We are here not only to visit you,

00:25:10.200 --> 00:25:11.460
but also to tell you something.

00:25:13.020 --> 00:25:14.420
That day in Sushui City,

00:25:15.280 --> 00:25:17.560
Prince Zhao's youngest son
who was hunting down Jicai

00:25:17.900 --> 00:25:19.960
came specifically to the dungeon
to interrogate us

00:25:20.100 --> 00:25:21.220
and asked us if we knew

00:25:21.220 --> 00:25:22.420
your secrets.

00:25:22.500 --> 00:25:24.260
There are things about you
that can be said,

00:25:24.260 --> 00:25:25.500
and things that cannot be said.

00:25:25.980 --> 00:25:27.900
We didn't know what should be said

00:25:27.900 --> 00:25:29.060
and what should not be said.

00:25:29.300 --> 00:25:30.220
I just thought

00:25:30.220 --> 00:25:31.180
you told me

00:25:31.180 --> 00:25:32.460
that Prince Zhao knows

00:25:32.460 --> 00:25:33.540
your true identity.

00:25:35.920 --> 00:25:37.260
That day when you took off clothes

00:25:37.260 --> 00:25:38.260
in the carriage...

00:25:47.740 --> 00:25:48.740
It's not that.

00:25:49.100 --> 00:25:51.160
That day, Mr. Lin was wearing
his official uniform.

00:25:51.160 --> 00:25:52.340
He couldn't go to a restaurant

00:25:52.340 --> 00:25:53.460
wearing his official uniform.

00:25:53.460 --> 00:25:54.740
He could only change temporarily.

00:26:00.730 --> 00:26:03.540
Is she really so unconcerned about it?

00:26:04.100 --> 00:26:04.940
So

00:26:05.820 --> 00:26:07.660
you said you know my identity?

00:26:10.540 --> 00:26:11.380
Well,

00:26:12.300 --> 00:26:13.180
just to save my life,

00:26:13.180 --> 00:26:15.540
I still had to say something
they don't know,

00:26:15.820 --> 00:26:17.620
without affecting you.

00:26:18.740 --> 00:26:19.500
So I said

00:26:19.500 --> 00:26:21.540
you and the Princess
have an ambiguous relationship.

00:26:21.540 --> 00:26:23.220
Sorry for affecting your reputation.

00:26:32.140 --> 00:26:33.140
It's just reputation.

00:26:33.700 --> 00:26:35.400
It's better than letting them
hurt you...

00:26:39.580 --> 00:26:40.420
And you.

00:26:41.900 --> 00:26:43.100
It doesn't matter.

00:26:43.740 --> 00:26:44.980
After all, it's because of me

00:26:45.140 --> 00:26:46.660
that you had to suffer this calamity.

00:26:49.430 --> 00:26:50.300
Mr. Lin,

00:26:50.300 --> 00:26:51.500
we are all one family.

00:26:51.740 --> 00:26:52.820
No need to say such things.

00:26:53.300 --> 00:26:55.060
Actually, we all know in our hearts

00:26:55.060 --> 00:26:57.460
that you're trying to reverse the case
for the Cui family.

00:26:58.320 --> 00:26:59.190
- Yeah.
- Well,

00:26:59.620 --> 00:27:01.100
does Prince Zhao taking us as hostages

00:27:01.100 --> 00:27:02.820
have anything to do with it?

00:27:05.700 --> 00:27:07.720
Alright. If Mr. Lin doesn't want
to talk about it,

00:27:07.720 --> 00:27:08.780
we won't ask then.

00:27:10.140 --> 00:27:11.060
Don't worry.

00:27:11.300 --> 00:27:12.540
I will risk my life

00:27:12.540 --> 00:27:13.940
to protect you all.

00:27:13.950 --> 00:27:14.500
I know

00:27:14.500 --> 00:27:16.700
people's perception of life and death
is very different.

00:27:16.720 --> 00:27:18.730
They think many things
are more important than life.

00:27:18.740 --> 00:27:20.660
But you are like family to us.

00:27:21.200 --> 00:27:22.300
We only hope that our family

00:27:22.300 --> 00:27:23.700
can live well.

00:27:25.160 --> 00:27:26.620
Mr. Lin, let me say a few words too.

00:27:26.980 --> 00:27:28.900
As the head of this family...

00:27:35.140 --> 00:27:36.140
The head's husband.

00:27:36.540 --> 00:27:37.460
I make a statement.

00:27:37.820 --> 00:27:38.660
First of all,

00:27:39.140 --> 00:27:40.980
reversing the case
is extremely important.

00:27:41.260 --> 00:27:44.060
Secondly, Prince Zhao has been secretly
setting you up.

00:27:44.060 --> 00:27:44.980
Before we came here,

00:27:44.980 --> 00:27:46.460
we've discussed it in meetings.

00:27:46.460 --> 00:27:47.300
We decided

00:27:47.310 --> 00:27:49.140
to stand firmly by your side

00:27:49.140 --> 00:27:50.740
and help you to reverse the case.

00:27:50.900 --> 00:27:51.780
You can't.

00:27:51.780 --> 00:27:53.100
Why not?

00:27:53.140 --> 00:27:54.020
Well,

00:27:54.100 --> 00:27:55.820
ever since we arrived in Yong'an City,

00:27:55.820 --> 00:27:57.540
we've received a lot of help from you.

00:27:58.010 --> 00:27:59.410
And I can also tell

00:27:59.660 --> 00:28:00.500
all of this

00:28:00.660 --> 00:28:02.460
comes from the bottom of your heart.

00:28:02.580 --> 00:28:03.740
So we definitely won't

00:28:03.740 --> 00:28:04.980
leave you behind and ignore you.

00:28:05.100 --> 00:28:05.940
Exactly.

00:28:06.100 --> 00:28:06.980
Mr. Lin,

00:28:06.980 --> 00:28:08.600
there's one more thing
I want to ask you.

