After my extensive inquiries,

00:32:56.020 --> 00:32:56.940
I discovered

00:32:56.940 --> 00:32:58.140
the sworn brother of the son

00:32:58.140 --> 00:32:59.480
of the second aunt of the cousin

00:32:59.500 --> 00:33:00.740
of the wife of the third brother

00:33:00.740 --> 00:33:02.270
of that Aunt Ge who delivers fish to us

00:33:02.340 --> 00:33:02.780
is a member

00:33:03.380 --> 00:33:04.260
of the Jinwu Guards.

00:33:04.470 --> 00:33:05.580
They've been

00:33:05.580 --> 00:33:07.260
investigating the cat theft case.

00:33:15.900 --> 00:33:17.300
Why are you looking at me like that?

00:33:18.100 --> 00:33:19.700
His Majesty lost his cat.

00:33:19.700 --> 00:33:20.900
That's a cat, after all.

00:33:21.140 --> 00:33:22.700
Isn't this already big news?

00:33:22.700 --> 00:33:24.900
This cat has already been found.

