The Crown Prince liked it,

00:33:26.200 --> 00:33:27.960
so he secretly took it away
for a few days.

00:33:28.040 --> 00:33:29.790
His Majesty has already
given him a lesson.

00:33:30.620 --> 00:33:31.460
By the way, Mr. Lin,

00:33:31.820 --> 00:33:32.940
I found out

