He doesn't want his granddaughter
to repeat the same mistake.

00:33:46.900 --> 00:33:48.340
Mr. Meng also mentioned it to me.

00:33:57.140 --> 00:33:58.180
Marriage?

00:33:58.520 --> 00:33:59.620
Did you agree?

